      		<p>      			
      			<lb n="3"/><supplied reason="undefined">Āḷu</supplied> mīvēṇ<choice><orig>n</orig><reg>ṇ</reg></choice>āṭu
      			<lb n="4"/>ci<choice><orig>r</orig><reg>ṟ</reg></choice>u<choice><orig>p</orig><reg>pp</reg></choice>pāḻ Āḷ
      			<lb n="5" break="no"/>vār pālāciriru mak
      			<lb n="6" break="no"/>kaḷ māṟaṉ ka<supplied reason="undefined">pe</supplied>
      			<lb n="7" break="no"/>ūru toṟu koṇ
      			<lb n="8" break="no"/><supplied reason="undefined">ṭa</supplied> ñāṉṟu paṭṭā
      			<lb n="9" break="no"/>ṉ kal
      		</p>
      		
